OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA fine start, with bright or
OL,6,Fsunny spells. However, cloud gradually
OL,7,Fthickening from the west, with some
OL,8,Frain possible in the far west.
OL,9,FOtherwise staying mostly fine until
OL,10,Fthe evening, with heavy showers then
OL,11,Fspreading east.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FCloudy with showers becoming
OL,14,Fwidespread through the evening, and
OL,15,Flikely merging into more persistent
OL,16,Fand occasionally heavy rain. Rain only
OL,17,Ferratically clearing east after dawn,
OL,18,Fbut with further showers following.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
